        <div class="hospice-text">
            <h3>How Hospice Support Works</h3>
            <p>When you opt for hospice care, our team will work closely with you and your family to create a personalized care plan that meets your needs while honoring and accommodating your preferences. Whether you are at home or in a care facility, we’re here to ensure your comfort and support every step of the way.</p>
        </div>
