        </div>
        <div class="hospice-text">
            <h3>Our Interdisciplinary Care Team Includes:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Doctors and nurse practitioners</li>
                <li>Counselors and social workers</li>
                <li>Physical, occupational, speech and respiratory therapists</li>
                <li>Nutritionists and dieticians</li>
                <li>Hospice aides and homemakers</li>
                <li>Volunteers</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You and your loved ones will have 24/7 access to hospice nurses and doctors who are available to provide care and answer questions at any time.</p>
            <p>You can choose to include your regular doctor, a nurse practitioner, or a physician assistant as part of your hospice care team to ensure continuity and familiarity.</p>
            <p>Our hospice services are designed to help families stay together in the comfort of home. If inpatient care becomes necessary, we will coordinate all arrangements to ensure a smooth transition and continued support.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

