        <div class="hospice-text">
            <h3>Who Can Receive Hospice Care (Eligibility)</h3>
            <p>To be eligible for hospice care, individuals must meet specific criteria where a Medical Doctor must confirm a terminal diagnosis. If you or a loved one are facing a concern regarding your serious illness and wish to have the condition managed at the place you live, our team can help determine if hospice is the right option.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hospice-img">
