            <h3>Eligibility includes:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>A certification from your hospice doctor (or your regular doctor, if applicable, and should you wish to remain in the picture) confirming a terminal illness with a limited life expectancy.</li>
                <li>Agreement to receive comfort-focused (palliative) care instead of aggressive treatment options.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
